<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,306,813,838]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Remarks</emphasis>
. We have included our species in the subgenus 
<taxonomicName authority="Dall, 1908" authorityName="Dall" authorityYear="1908" box="[858,1098,813,838]" class="Bivalvia" family="Solemyidae" genus="Solemya" kingdom="Animalia" order="Solemyoida" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Mollusca" rank="subGenus" subGenus="Petrasma">
<emphasis box="[858,966,814,837]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Petrasma</emphasis>
